        <!-- required for collection level; optional for lower levels -->
        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">

            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>The Domherr mss., 1937-1975, consists of papers of Russian editor and translator
                Ludwig Leopoldovich Domherr, 1894- . Present in the collection are notes and
                transcriptions of letters of Alexander Herzen prepared by Domherr for publication,
                as well as newspaper clippings about Domherr's work on the Herzen letters. Most of
                the material is in Russian.</p>
        </scopecontent>

